# Frontend Structure for TanStack Start Project

## Project Overview

This document outlines the recommended directory structure for a small to medium-sized TanStack Start project with React, TypeScript, and shadcn/ui. The structure separates routes from features and organizes API calls, hooks, and UI components for optimal maintainability and scalability.

